### Key Design Decisions

| Decision | Rationale |
|----------|-----------|
| All code in `lib.rs` | Project convention — no separate module files |
| `serde(rename_all = "lowercase")` on enum | Matches frontend camelCase convention |
| Status = **last occurring event** | Fixes issue-28 (resume) and issue-34 (cleanup interrupt) |
| `tokio::spawn_blocking` for I/O | Follows existing command pattern |
| `Option<u32>` for score/timing | Handles incomplete workflows gracefully |

